---
title: Southwest Stuffed Zucchini Boats with Plant-based Protein, Pico de Gallo & Avocado Crema
description: Send your taste buds on a flavorful cruise—a yacht to Yumtown, if you will—with this crowd-pleasing stuffed zucchini. These boats are filled with Southwest-spiced rice, then blanketed with a layer of kickin’ pepper jack cheese, and finished with fresh pico de gallo, avocado crema, cilantro, sour cream, and hot sauce. There’s something about this recipe that’ll really put the wind back in your sails.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/61df167ffa3e764d4b2c785a-787a7e13.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/southwest-stuffed-zucchini-boats-61df167ffa3e764d4b2c785a-0565221e.pdf
cuisine: Mexican
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/southwest-stuffed-zucchini-boats-61df167ffa3e764d4b2c785a
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 790 kcal
  fat: 42 g
  saturated fat: 18 g
  carbohydrates: 81 g
  sugar: 16 g
  protein: 30 g
